  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You glance into the future to give yourself enough information to make the right move to reduce the chance of suffering a debilitating effect. you gain advantage on all saving throws until the start of your next turn. </p><p>Beginning at 7th level, you can instead choose to gain a +5 bonus to AC, until the beginning of your next turn. Beginning at 18th level you can foresee the worst future and react to prevent it. The next hostile attack or effect would reduce your hit points to 0 is avoided as you gain immunity to the attack or effect until the end of the current turn.</p>",
